ZH: 我们计划明年夏天下乡度假。
EN: We plan to go rural for a vacation next summer.

ZH: 他打算报名参加下月的下乡活动。
EN: He intends to sign up for the rural activity next month.

ZH: 政府鼓励年轻人下乡工作。
EN: The government encourages young people to work in rural areas.

ZH: 我明年毕业后想暂时下乡支教。
EN: After graduation next year, I want to temporarily teach in the countryside.

ZH: 据说下乡有助于缓解城市生活的压力。
EN: It is said that going rural helps relieve the stress of city life.

ZH: 这个项目让志愿者有机会下乡实地调研。
EN: This project provides volunteers an opportunity to conduct on-site research in rural areas.

ZH: 我们家祖辈都是农村出身，我很向往下乡的生活。
EN: My ancestors were all from rural areas, and I yearn for a rural life.

ZH: 他每年都会组织一次下乡写生活动。
EN: He organizes a rural sketching activity every year.

ZH: 下乡让我更加懂得农民辛勤劳动的重要性。
EN: Going rural made me understand the importance of farmers' hard work even more.

ZH: 这次我去下乡体验了种地、放牛、捕鱼等活动。
EN: This time I went rural and experienced activities such as farming, herding cows, and fishing.

ZH: 下乡的路很曲折，但风景很美。
EN: The road to the countryside is winding, but the scenery is beautiful.

ZH: 近几年，越来越多的人选择下乡养老。
EN: In recent years, more and more people have chosen to retire in rural areas.

ZH: 这次下乡活动有助于增进城乡之间的交流与理解。
EN: This rural activity helps enhance communication and understanding between urban and rural areas.

ZH: 下乡之前，我需要学习一些基本的农事知识。
EN: Before going rural, I need to learn some basic agricultural knowledge.

ZH: 她接受了一个志愿者的机会，到贫困地区下乡支教。
EN: She seized a volunteer opportunity to teach in rural areas in impoverished regions.

ZH: 年轻人下乡是为了寻找更自由的生活方式。
EN: Young people go rural in search of a more freedom-filled lifestyle.

ZH: 这个项目的目的是激励青年人下乡发展农业产业。
EN: The objective of this project is to motivate young people to develop agricultural industries in rural areas.

ZH: 她每个暑假都会选择下乡帮助当地的农民。
EN: Every summer vacation, she chooses to go rural and help local farmers.

ZH: 这个农场提供给游客下乡体验的机会。
EN: This farm offers tourists an opportunity to experience rural life.

ZH: 下乡让我对农民辛勤劳作的精神有了更深的理解。
EN: Going rural has given me a deeper understanding of the hardworking spirit of farmers.
